<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><key>B</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Zesuh, nangmah na ttha bik, Zesuh khuaruahhar na si
 Halleluijah, Min vialte lak ah, Na min thiang kan in thangthat
 Kan sinah na um, Bawi Jesuh.

[V2]
 Zesuh, nangmah na lian bik, Zesuh a Lian bik na si
 Halleluijah, Min vialte lak ah, Na min thiang kan in thangthat
 Kan sinah na um, Bawi Jesuh.

[V3]
 Zesuh, nangmah na Tthawng bik, Zesuh a Tthawng bik na si
 Halleluijah, Min vialte lak ah, Na min thiang kan in thangthat
 Kan sinah na um, Bawi Jesuh.

[V4]
 Zesuh, nangmah na Thiang bik, Zesuh a Thiang bik na si
 Halleluijah, Min vialte lak ah, Na min thiang kan in thangthat
 Kan sinah na um Bawi jesuh.

[V5]
 Zesuh, Thangthat tlak na si, Zesuh Thangthat tlak na si
 Halleluijah, Min vialte lak ah, Na min thiang kan in thangthat
 Kan sinah na um, bawi Jesuh.</lyrics>
<title>ZESUH NANGMAH NA TTHA BIK</title>
</song>